data.description: Completely updated 2 Story Home! Spacious main level with large living area, dining room, updated kitchen with loads of counter space, cabinets & walk in pantry. Main level also boasts a full bath and mudroom area off rear of home. Upstairs you will find 3 spacious bedrooms and a 2nd full bath that has been completed updated complete with tile shower surround. Level fenced backyard features a pergola and direct access to your own oversized 1 car garage! Per seller 2023 updates include; roof, siding, windows/doors, furnace/AC, remodeled baths, plumbing, electrical, & paint! Nothing to do here but MOVE IN!
